title: No Limits 2 Roller Coaster [MAC OS X]
description:
I have converted this windows game to mac with Wineskin, and works perfectly, hope you like it, comment.

System Requirements:

- 100% OpenGL-compatible graphics card with at least 32MB RAM
  Tested with the following chipsets: G400/G450/G550*, TNT2, GeForce1/2/3/4/5/6/7*,
  Rage128*, Radeon* 
  Tested by me with Intel GMA X3100**

- MAC OS X 10.6 Snow Leopard and Above

- 128MB RAM (256MB recommended) Tested with 3GB RAM

- DirectX 5 or newer (DirectX 9 recommended)

- 586-family processor (Pentium 3 or better recommended) 1.2GHz Dual-core or 2.2GHz single-core and above.
Tested on Intel Core 2 Duo 2GHz

- 16bit sound card
